author: @Necroherz
text:
First of all, it makes me so angry that my Jaehyunie had to see his first promotions as a soloist being diluted to a such a short amount of time. He really wanted to show us a lot and make it memorable but that ex team mate, that moth3rfvcker, ruined everything but our Jaehyun still kept going, was actually the first one to make a public appearance since the news broke... but it was good to see the staff was still the same, everyone treated him with attention and love, Johnny went to see him, the music show gave him a gift, the nctzens who went to watch him there in person cheered on him really loud and you can tell that at least the k-side of our fandom is still supporting our neos as strongly as before. It's just the trolls and rat coming under rock who are slandering and spreading misinformation on the neos who has nothing to do with that guy private affairs (Crimes)... Srsly i hate the fact Jaehyun could have and enjoy the whole process of having a solo debut. Like the promotions, the interviews, the challenges with his members and other idols... It breaks my heart...
Second of all, it is so nerve wracking to have to see my man (And Johnny too) having to put a smile on his face and pretend nothing was happening at that moment because he was promoting and everyone of us, the group, we nctzens and social medias were on fire 🥺
